Motormaster let out a cry of rage, and through himself forward in a full
dash, sticking his blade out in front of him as he ran towards Megatron.

Megatron steped back, bracing himself. He flung his mace up, and with his
other hand, grabed the end off it, and held the chain up in front off him
as a shield, to block the blow. The sword hit hard against the chain, a
large electric noise emmiting from the grinding of metal against pure
energy. "You are as strong as Megatron"
